    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this absolute gem go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in a garage and pampered since day one, so it still has that fresh, new-car feel inside and out. The paint is flawless and it drives like a total dream! If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
