    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Titanium Silver. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-overhead cam design with double-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear 8,000 RPM power band. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed to the highest standard, including rod bearing replacement, valve clearance adjustment, and a reinforced rear subframe carrier panel. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic turn-in characteristic of the E46 chassis. With zero paint correction needed and a clean undercarriage free of oxidation, this is a turnkey example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Immaculate condition. Original paint. Interior flawless. Full service history. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
