    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in absolute showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips or imperfections, having been strictly garage-kept and hand-washed only. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and the 'new car' scent is still present. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at certified dealerships. With exceptionally low mileage and a smooth, powerful drive that feels exactly as it did on the delivery floor, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a spotless vehicle history report.",
      "price": 48500.0,
