    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. The engine's individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing operate with factory precision, delivering a linear torque curve and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission offers tight, mechanical shifts, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to maintain optimal chassis kinematics under load. Every bushing, seal, and dampening component remains in peak operational condition, ensuring the original handling geometry is preserved. The exterior finish and interior upholstery show no signs of the typical wear associated with the chassis, making this a true collector-grade specimen for the discerning driver.",
